006/**
007 * The color constants from SColor, but without extending color or storing names.
008 *
009 * This is useful for editors like IntelliJ IDEA that show Color (but not SColor) easily.
010 *
011 * Has some built in palettes available as Color arrays.
012 *
013 * @author Eben Howard - http://squidpony.com - howard@squidpony.com
014 * @author Tommy Ettinger
015 */
